# EV Battery Recommendation System ⚡

An AI-powered web application that recommends optimal EV batteries based on user constraints such as budget, range, charging time, and warranty.

## Features
- Dynamic filtering
- Data visualization
- Downloadable reports
- Interactive UI (Gradio)

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- Gradio
- Matplotlib

## Live Demo
https://ev-battery-recommendation.onrender.com/
